explicit installs
* efibootmgr
* lsblk
* niri
* flatpak (see below)
* xdg-desktop-portal
* xdg-document-portal (see below)
* pipewire
* wireplumber
* pipewire-pulse


dependencies
* flatpak installs xdg-dbus-proxy which installs dbus
* flatpak installs fuse3 so there's no reason not to install xdg-document-portal
